tool_description: Easily get TikTok's Trending / Discover Data! (Trending Users / Trending Hashtags / Trending Songs)
title: TikTok Trending Data

api_list.name: /t
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://tiktok-trending-data.p.rapidapi.com/t"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "tiktok-trending-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
